{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二回　安乐公子。剑客行故事继续。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着，他刚好走到厉文豹身侧，就将手中的那只盖碗一扬，带笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着又走到厉文虎身前，含笑接道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "主人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他目光突地一凛，瞪在厉文虎身上，接着又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敝兄弟虽然是武林中的无名小卒，可是，敝兄弟的居停主人却不是普普通通的武林道，江湖中人多多少少也得给他三分面子，只是——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一掉头，朝那此刻站在旁边已心安理得的胖灵官冷笑说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕云五霸天",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我厉文虎今日被这样作践，这只怪我姓厉的学艺不精，但——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓厉的，你——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "安乐公子最风流",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铮兄清玩，樊非拜赠",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他朗声一笑，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕云五霸天",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕云五霸天",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他语声微顿，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四大公子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "微微一顿，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你管不着！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一面却侧过头，朝那已转到展白身后的瘦小老者道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他哈哈一笑，指着这瘦小老者向展白道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第一神偷追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
