      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着，他一面嘿嘿冷笑，胸膛挺得更高，两只大眼睛瞪得滚圆，发着光，一面又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
